{"title":"Tout Terrain Ceres GT is Adventure Brand’s Fastest, Lightest Steel Gravel Bike","link":"https://bikerumor.com/tout-terrain-ceres-gt-fast-steel-gravel-bike/","date":1733403600000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_detail-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"2025 Tout Terrain Ceres GT fast steel gravel bike\" /></p>\n<p>Tout Terrain, who we know best for their adventure-ready and world-touring steel bikes, now has a new fast all-surface Ceres gravel &amp; all-road bike. Don’t worry, it’s still steel and still built for the long haul. But now you can pick up more speed and feel more wind in your face on a Tout Terrain built for all-day rides, ultra-distances, and high pace gravel racing.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Tout Terrain Ceres GT fast steel gravel bike</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_still-adventure-ready-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_still-adventure-ready-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Tout Terrain Ceres GT fast steel gravel bike, still adventure-ready\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_still-adventure-ready-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_still-adventure-ready-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_still-adventure-ready-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_still-adventure-ready-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_still-adventure-ready-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_still-adventure-ready-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Tout Terrain)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There’s a lot that sets the new Ceres apart from Tout Terrain’s standard adventure style bikes. It features more race-focused geometry, with a lower bar position, longer reach, and steeper headtube angle. Plus, it features a thin-wall triple-butted steel frame with slightly dropped seat stays that Tout Terrain says provides a balance of lightweight, durability, and a classic steel ride for all-day comfort, even when you are riding quickly.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_seat-cluster-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_seat-cluster-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Tout Terrain Ceres GT fast steel gravel bike, seat cluster detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_seat-cluster-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_seat-cluster-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_seat-cluster-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_seat-cluster-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_seat-cluster-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_seat-cluster-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_seat-cluster-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>developed for fast all-road and gravel road riding and racing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>triple-butted, heat-treated Thermocrom 4130 chromoly steel frame </li>\n\n\n\n<li>lower carbon footprint for vs. Tout Terrain’s comparable Dedacciai tubing “<em>due to a reduction in the shipment of the raw materials and tubing between countries</em>“</li>\n\n\n\n<li>full carbon suspension-corrected Gravel Fork SL with threaded anything cage bosses, 405mm axle-to-crown</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_internal-routing-detail-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_internal-routing-detail-1536x1536.webp\" alt=\"2025 Tout Terrain Ceres GT fast steel gravel bike, internal routing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_internal-routing-detail-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_internal-routing-detail-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_internal-routing-detail-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_internal-routing-detail-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_internal-routing-detail-jpg.webp 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_T47-BB-detail-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_T47-BB-detail-1536x1536.webp\" alt=\"2025 Tout Terrain Ceres GT fast steel gravel bike, T47 BB\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_T47-BB-detail-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_T47-BB-detail-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_T47-BB-detail-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_T47-BB-detail-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_T47-BB-detail-jpg.webp 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_NDS-dropout-detail-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_NDS-dropout-detail-1536x1536.webp\" alt=\"2025 Tout Terrain Ceres GT fast steel gravel bike, dropout\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_NDS-dropout-detail-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_NDS-dropout-detail-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_NDS-dropout-detail-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_NDS-dropout-detail-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_NDS-dropout-detail-jpg.webp 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>internal cable routing through modular port in the downtube (non-driveside)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>includes stealth internal dropper &amp; dynamo taillight routing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>T47 threaded bottom bracket</li>\n\n\n\n<li>UDH derailleur compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_rear-end-detail-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_rear-end-detail-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Tout Terrain Ceres GT fast steel gravel bike, drivestrain detail UDH\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_rear-end-detail-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_rear-end-detail-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_rear-end-detail-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_rear-end-detail-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_rear-end-detail-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_rear-end-detail-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_rear-end-detail-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>oversized, reinforced 44mm headtube for tapered steerers</li>\n\n\n\n<li>27.2mm seatpost</li>\n\n\n\n<li>signature Tout Terrain Ergo-Stop II steering stop </li>\n\n\n\n<li>flat mount 160.. disc brakes &amp; 12mm thru-axles</li>\n\n\n\n<li>max 54mm 700c/29er tire clearance</li>\n\n\n\n<li>2x 3-pack anything cage and 3x conventional cage / bag mounts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>frame rack and fender mounts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>available in 4 sizes (S-XL)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_geometry-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_geometry-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Tout Terrain Ceres GT fast steel gravel bike, geometry\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_geometry-jpg.webp 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_geometry-297x165.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_geometry-1536x853.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_geometry-120x67.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_geometry-768x427.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tout Terrain Ceres – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_complete-Apex-GX-AXS-mullet-build-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_complete-Apex-GX-AXS-mullet-build-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Tout Terrain Ceres GT fast steel gravel bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_complete-Apex-GX-AXS-mullet-build-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_complete-Apex-GX-AXS-mullet-build-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_complete-Apex-GX-AXS-mullet-build-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_complete-Apex-GX-AXS-mullet-build-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_complete-Apex-GX-AXS-mullet-build-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>2025 Tout Terrain Ceres GT SRAM Apex/GX AXS</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Ceres GT can be configured starting today <a href=\"https://tout-terrain.de/en/the-products/bicycles/x.over/ceres/\" target=\"_blank\">on Tout Terrain’s website</a>, where you can pick stock or custom colors, tweak some of the components, and add accessories. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>But essentially, this new Tout Terrain Ceres GT is only offered in one SRAM Apex/GX AXS  Eagle Mullet group build for now with a rigid carbon fork starting at 3800€ complete, at a claimed 10.5kg. Officially though, not yet with the Cane Creek Invert suspension fork we see in all of these nice riding photos. However, we expect that suspension fork upgrade will be available through your local dealer.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_forest-road-riding-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_forest-road-riding-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Tout Terrain Ceres GT fast steel gravel bike, forest road riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_forest-road-riding-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_forest-road-riding-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_forest-road-riding-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_forest-road-riding-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Tout-Terrain-Ceres-GT-fast-steel-gravel-bike_forest-road-riding-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new fast steel gravel bike will only be available to pick up from your local Tout Terrain bike shop, with the first Ceres builds arriving this coming Spring, in “Q2 2025”.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://Tout-Terrain.de/en/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Tout-Terrain.de/en</em></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/tout-terrain-ceres-gt-fast-steel-gravel-bike/\">Tout Terrain Ceres GT is Adventure Brand’s Fastest, Lightest Steel Gravel Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"e2cfe6574091a34c015f5882009984b92a030159c36f6f1dab9e61d0db1e2ee2","category":"Cycling"}